parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbags to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the occupants of the vehicle are not provided with the necessary protection.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
warning lights illuminate on the dashboard
airbag light stays on
and the vehicle is involved in an accident with no airbag deployment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended airbag deployment can cause injuries, accidents, or distractions while driving, and may lead to a loss of control of the vehicle.
symptoms: Airbags deploy unexpectedly
without a crash or impact
while the vehicle is in motion or stationary
and the deployment can cause injuries or distractions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which may lead to a failure to deploy in a crash or unintended deployment.
symptoms: Airbag warning light stays on
airbag light illuminates on the dashboard
and the vehicle may have a faulty airbag module or clock spring issue.
